snippet: San Marino, joint bottom of the world rankings alongside Bhutan, ended a run of 61 consecutive defeats in all competitions when they held Estonia to a goalless draw in their Euro 2016 qualifier on Saturday....
lead_paragraph: San Marino, joint bottom of the world rankings alongside Bhutan, ended a run of 61 consecutive defeats in all competitions when they held Estonia to a goalless draw in their Euro 2016 qualifier on Saturday.
